  <article id="comment-1055396" class="single-comment">
    <div>
      <header>
        <div>
                      <a href="/users/james-wenska/comments" title="View James Wenska&#039;s profile">James Wenska</a>                                <time class="created" title="2011-09-27T03:30:57+00:00">Sep 27th 2011 3:30 GMT</time>
        </div>
      </header>
      <div class="comment-body"><p>If this sort of technology becomes mainstream it's possible that with this accuracy level traffic jams and gas consumption could drop considerably, and as a result gas prices could fall. In fact if new technologies based off of this were made so that phones using this app could interact with one another, it could obsolete traffic lights entirely.</p>
</div>
