      <header>
        <div>
                      <a href="/users/gcguard5/comments" title="View gcguard5&#039;s profile">gcguard5</a>                                <time class="created" title="2011-09-24T14:33:40+00:00">Sep 24th 2011 14:33 GMT</time>
        </div>
      </header>
      <div class="comment-body"><p>Every driver tries to play the game of catching every green light so this APP does a couple good things for drivers on the road. First off, the APP allows you to save fuel which of course saves money and who doesn't like saving money? Second, it makes your driving more productive and less aggravating. Driving isn't so frustrating when your constantly moving, it's the stop and go that bugs people. Third, it improves safety on the road because it won't have as many drivers speeding up to catch that yellow light. It will also make it safer because you will see more people driving slower, based on the SignalGuru's recommended speed in order to catch the next light. An all around good idea for an application, and given its recent statistics, it actually works!</p>
</div>
