      </article>



  <article id="comment-1046681" class="single-comment">
    <div>
      <header>
        <div>
                      <a href="/users/zellergvtedu/comments" title="View zellerg@vt.edu&#039;s profile">zellerg@vt.edu</a>                                <time class="created" title="2011-09-21T02:40:31+00:00">Sep 21st 2011 2:40 GMT</time>
        </div>
      </header>
      <div class="comment-body"><p>Unless this technology were to be installed during manufacturing than an APP, although cheap, would feed that social monster we like to call distracted driving. I believe that this technology would help somewhat but it would not be enough to counterbalance the safety factor.</p>
</div>
      <footer class="clearfix">
                  <ul class="links"><li class="comment_recommend first"><a href="/vote/recommend-comment/1046681?token=c5abfde555fbb44cff9d7f05c48146d1&amp;nid=21528910&amp;page=0&amp;sort=0" title="Recommend comment: Unless this technology were" class="recommend" data-ec-omniture="recommend_comment" rel="nofollow">Recommend</a> <div><span>1</span></div></li>
<li class="comment_report_abuse"><a href="/report-abuse/comment/21528910/1046681?destination=node%2F21528910" title="Report this comment to our moderators" class="report-anchor secondary-action" data-form-ajax="/ajax/report-abuse/comment/21528910/1046681" rel="nofollow">Report</a></li>
<li class="permalink"><a href="http://www.economist.com/comment/1046681#comment-1046681" title="Permanent link to this comment" rel="nofollow" class=" secondary-action">Permalink</a></li>
<li class="comment_reply last"><a href="/comment/reply/21528910/1046681" data-form-ajax="/ajax/comment/reply/21528910/1046681">reply</a></li>
</ul>              </footer>
    </div>
      </article>



  <article id="comment-1045721" class="single-comment">
    <div>
      <header>
        <div>
                      <a href="/users/stevekeck2/comments" title="View stevekeck2&#039;s profile">stevekeck2</a>                                <time class="created" title="2011-09-20T15:58:54+00:00">Sep 20th 2011 15:58 GMT</time>
        </div>
      </header>
      <div class="comment-body"><p>This is brilliant.  Smart phones are becoming more popular everyday and more and more people are buying them.  Using them to help with traffic situations like rush hour could do much more than avoid accidents and help save gas.  This could impact everything from shipping and receiving to gas prices.  If this technology could be implemented in every new car being built instead of just in smart phones it could impact the entire world and not just the United States.  Hopefully this will catch on and continue to be tested.</p>
</div>
      <footer class="clearfix">
                  <ul class="links"><li class="comment_recommend first"><a href="/vote/recommend-comment/1045721?token=6d562c55cdfeccb69a79ceb92ba06fa7&amp;nid=21528910&amp;page=0&amp;sort=0" title="Recommend comment: This is brilliant.  Smart" class="recommend" data-ec-omniture="recommend_comment" rel="nofollow">Recommend</a> <div><span>1</span></div></li>
