  <article id="comment-1045406" class="single-comment">
    <div>
      <header>
        <div>
                      <a href="/users/katied09/comments" title="View katied09&#039;s profile">katied09</a>                                <time class="created" title="2011-09-20T12:30:41+00:00">Sep 20th 2011 12:30 GMT</time>
        </div>
      </header>
      <div class="comment-body"><p>This technology seems really cool, but aren't distracted drivers (if not the #1 reason) one of the top reasons for traffic crashes and fatalities? It would be nice if we could find quicker and easier ways through traffic, but it isn't worth the risk of wrecking and then backing up traffic even more than the light would.</p>
</div>
