                  <ul class="links"><li class="comment_recommend first"><a href="/vote/recommend-comment/1044886?token=d26aaef3ce7dea1beb0d30e8f4c27ac1&amp;nid=21528910&amp;page=0&amp;sort=0" title="Recommend comment: Its good to know that today" class="recommend" data-ec-omniture="recommend_comment" rel="nofollow">Recommend</a> <div><span>1</span></div></li>
<li class="comment_report_abuse"><a href="/report-abuse/comment/21528910/1044886?destination=node%2F21528910" title="Report this comment to our moderators" class="report-anchor secondary-action" data-form-ajax="/ajax/report-abuse/comment/21528910/1044886" rel="nofollow">Report</a></li>
